<main>

<section>
    <h2>Helpful Tips</h2>

    <h3>1. Pack Light</h3>
    <p>Carry only what you need for easy travel.</p>

    <h3>2. Keep Documents Safe</h3>
    <p>Always have copies of your passport.</p>

    <h3>3. Learn Basic Phrases</h3>
    <p>Helps communicate in different countries.</p>

    <h3>4. Stay Hydrated</h3>
    <p>Drink enough water during your trip.</p>

    <h3>5. Plan Ahead</h3>
    <p>Book hotels and tickets early.</p>

</section>

<aside>
    <p>Tip: Always check the weather before traveling!</p>
